Name: HubSpot CRM Deals
Description: Work with deals in the HubSpot CRM
Tools: Create Deal, Get Deal, Delete Deal, Update Deal, Search Deals
Share Context: HubSpot CRM Context from ./tool.gpt
Tools: ./associations.gpt, ./properties.gpt, ./owners.gpt
Params: prompt: detailed request to be executed against the HubSpot API


Fulfill the users request: ${PROMPT}

Use the tools available to you.

---
Name: Create Deal
Description: Creates a new deal in the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: properties: a json object with all the properties of the deal

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/createDeal.py

---
Name: Get Deal
Description: Retrieves a deal by ID from the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: deal_id: the ID of the deal to retrieve

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/getDeal.py

---
Name: Delete Deal
Description: Deletes a deal by ID from the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: deal_id: the ID of the deal to delete

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/deleteDeal.py

---
Name: Update Deal
Description: Updates an existing deal in the HubSpot CRM by ID
Credential: ./credential
Params: deal_id: the ID of the deal to update
Params: properties: a json object with all the properties of the deal

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/updateDeal.py

---
Name: Search Deals
Description: Searches for deals in the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: filters: a json object with one or more keys in the format `{"<PROPERTY_NAME>":"<VALUE_TO_SEARCH_FOR>"}`. Each key in the json must be a valid property name returned by the 'HubSpot CRM Get Properties' tool.

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/searchDeals.py
